{{if .sample_test_result}}
{{if eq .sample_test_result "pass"}}
### ✅ Laboratory Test Passed

The laboratory analysis has been completed. No quarantine pests were detected.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Result**: 🟢 Pass — No Quarantine Pests Found
{{if .lab_comments}}* **Laboratory Notes**: {{.lab_comments}}{{end}}
{{if .lab_report_attachment_url}}* **Lab Report**: [View Report]({{.lab_report_attachment_url}}){{end}}
{{if .post_lab_visual_required}}* **⚠️ Additional Visual Inspection**: The airport PQS officer has requested a consignment visual inspection before proceeding.{{end}}
{{else if eq .sample_test_result "fail_resubmit"}}
### ⚠️ Laboratory Test Failed — Resubmission Allowed

The laboratory analysis detected quarantine pests or failed quality thresholds. You may submit a new sample for a second test.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Result**: 🔴 Fail — Resubmission Permitted
{{if .lab_comments}}* **Laboratory Notes**: {{.lab_comments}}{{end}}

Please proceed to the sample collection step to submit a new sample.
{{else if eq .sample_test_result "fail_final"}}
### 🔴 Laboratory Test Failed — Consignment Rejected

The laboratory analysis on the resubmitted sample has also failed. The consignment cannot proceed for a phytosanitary certificate.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Result**: 🔴 Final Failure — Consignment Rejected
{{if .lab_comments}}* **Laboratory Notes**: {{.lab_comments}}{{end}}
{{end}}
{{else}}
### ⏳ Laboratory Testing in Progress

The consignment sample is currently undergoing laboratory diagnostics at the PQS/NPQS laboratory.

* **Sample Number**: `{{.sample_number}}`
* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`

No action is required from you at this stage. You will be notified once the results are available.
{{end}}
